# Inverse Source EM

This repository contains code for the forward and inverse source problem in
cylindrical electromagnetic scattering. It combines analytical solvers
(PhysicsTM) with neural surrogate models (SurrogateEM) and classification
networks for estimating the number of internal sources.

The project is currently in the process of being migrated from Jupyter
notebooks to a clean, modular Python codebase.
